title: O'NEILL TNT COMP VEST
description:
Our compression molded TNT vest offers our exclusive floating
zipper closure that hides the belts, minimizes foam bulk and
maximizes fit adjust-ability. Flexibility is key to a good molded vest,
so each panel is segmented for maximum freedom and comfort
